							<h2>Netflix Theatre App Concept</h2>
							<p>
								<span class="palt paltspacing paltcolor">
									UX Design - Personal Project
								</span>
							</p>
							<span class="palt">
							<p>A course project done during my time obtaining my graduate degree at DePaul University. This project asked the question, "What if Netflix wanted to enter the movie theatre market?" Goals for the project included effective promotion, 
							providing detailed information and media for new and upcoming releases, and a reason for users to continuously interact with the app.	
						</p>
						</span>
							<span class="palt paltcolor paltspacing">
								<strong>Tools:</strong> &nbsp;  Figma, Adobe Photoshop
